short_summary: The Department of National Defence seeks a Senior Business Architect and Intermediate Courseware Developer to assist in developing and conducting training courses in SIGINT and Cyberspace Operations.
description: J7 Signals Intelligence (SIGINT) and Cyber Operations Training Team within the Canadian Forces Information Operations Group (CFIOG) has a requirement for one Senior Business Architect and one Intermediate Courseware Developer to assist in developing and conducting the Military SIGINT Managers (MSM) course, the Cyber Domain Basics (CDB) course,
